{{italics title}} {{Infobox circus | name = ''Circus 1903'' | image = | caption = | circus_name = | country = {{USA}} | founder = | year = | operator = | fate = | ringmaster = | director = | traveling = Formerly | tent = No | number = | winter = | acts = | other = | website = {{url|http://circus1903.com/}} }} '''''Circus 1903''''' is an American [[contemporary circus]].<ref name=NYT>[https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/theater/review-in-circus-1903-a-littler-big-top-still-offers-some-thrills.html The New York Times]</ref><ref>[http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/theater/reviews/ct-circus-1903-review-ent-0323-20170322-column.html Chicago Tribune]</ref><ref>[http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/arts/la-et-cm-circus-1903-7-digits-review-20170219-htmlstory.html Los Angeles Times]</ref>
''Circus 1903'' originated as a touring show<ref name=NYT/> and in 2017 moved to the Paris Theater at the [[Paris Las Vegas]] [[hotel]] and [[casino]].<ref>[https://www.reviewjournal.com/entertainment/entertainment-columns/kats/circus-1903-moving-into-paris-las-vegas-theater/ Las Vegas Review-Journal]</ref>
