[http://cwa-web.org The Contemporary Wayang Archive] (CWA) is a [[digital archive]] of full length videos of new adaptations of [[Javanese people|Javanese]] [[Wayang Kulit]] (wayang kontemporer), with subtitles and notes.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cwa-web.org/cwa/about.php?l=en |title=About the CWA Project and Team |access-date=9 September 2016}}</ref> It is a project by the [[National University of Singapore]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fas.nus.edu.sg/ell/Research_Project_CWA.html |title=NUS Research Projects |access-date=9 September 2016}}</ref>
